Step 1: Create a student list
Step 2: Ask the user to insert students' names into the student list
Step 3: Asking user what the user wants to do to the student list
1) Delete a student from the list
2) Add a new student to the list
3) Modify a student's name
4) Display the student list
Step 4: Repeat step 3 until the user chooses to end
Step 5: Add validation and error prevention to every process
1) Delete or modify the student's name only when it is available
2) Show an error when there are no student names to be displayed

Advanced:
Step 6: Create a txt file to store the student name list
